{"tid":2097823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「東廠」基地曝光　傳選定銅鑼灣酒店","createTime":"2020-07-07T05:25:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T15:10:12.000Z","uid":184679,"like":140,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"1639205c9298ba8dbca2cfc36dc0f27f1aa59934","tid":2097823,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:25:29.000Z","msg":"中國國務院日前（3日）宣佈任命駐港國安公署署長人選，公署的臨時辦公室位置也曝光。香港有周刊爆出中央駐港「第四機構」國安公署將以銅鑼灣維景酒店作為臨時基地。銅鑼灣維景酒店今早（7/7）門口有大批軍裝警員戒備，大廳玻璃門已用圍板圍封，有工人在外牆進行維修。香港《蘋果》致電飯店查詢預訂房間事宜，前台職員稱飯店近期正進行維修，至少半年不會接收客人。記者今晨所見，該飯店已不見有住客，工人忙著維修及裝修，更有2、30名軍裝警員在場戒備，保安員更質疑前來了解的區議員「是否想違反國家法」，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200707/TGAVWAAV5RMQYMEY7IO6QHSP5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200707%2FTGAVWAAV5RMQYMEY7IO6QHSP5Q%2F&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=360ade2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200707%2FTGAVWAAV5RMQYMEY7IO6QHSP5Q%2F&h=b29c9482\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20200707/TGAVWAAV5RMQYMEY7IO6QHSP5Q/</a>"},{"pid":"571566e42eda2113ace46ec1444aefcfda907b6b","tid":2097823,"uid":53062,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:27:13.000Z","msg":"點解唔去四季酒店，可以請大陸富豪飲茶"},{"pid":"95ef13e2bfee42053b3929cdce244688a3d24ec1","tid":2097823,"uid":16775,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"個個渣住雞毛當令箭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保安都可以周圍凶人"},{"pid":"f1c3e833489358fb40c2992c12c8cd95b01fbad4","tid":2097823,"uid":90863,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會呀<br />\n搵間咁up dup既黎招待欽差大人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091b31f3a7392a502b63d4261b3dab3efd53893a","tid":2097823,"uid":13663,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"quote":{"pid":"571